3rd party code and licenses
===========================

The code in montager.py and centerplanes_stack.py was inspired by Matlab
similar functions present in Dr. Jeff Fessler's image reconstruction toolbox:
http://web.eecs.umich.edu/~fessler/irt/irt/graph/

The code in ortho_viewer.py is adapted from nibabel and is covered under an MIT
license, as reproduced here:

